snippet.title: AGENT SIMULATION - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Agent Simulation will be released as a demo soon 📣 Don't forget to add it to your wishlist on the steam page 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1708050/Agent_Simulation/

"AGENT SIMULATION" Description:
If you are a sharpshooter, you would be a great fit for us. Within a short period of time, select 3 options from the list and deal with your enemies. Do not forget that the ability of using time efficiently and aiming your targets are crucial. Complete each mission and earn an agent certification.
